<odoo>
    <data>


        <template id="rechnung_account_template8" inherit_id="account.report_invoice_document">

            <xpath expr="//div[@class='page']" position="replace">
                <div class="page">

                    <div class="oe_structure"/>

                    <h3 class="text-right" style="margin-right: 15px;">
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'out_invoice' and (o.state == 'open' or o.state == 'paid')">Rechnung
                        </span>
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'out_invoice' and o.state == 'draft'">Rechnung</span>
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'out_invoice' and o.state == 'cancel'">Rechnung</span>
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'out_refund'">Credit Note</span>
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'in_refund'">Vendor Credit Note</span>
                        <span t-if="o.type == 'in_invoice'">Eingangsrechnung</span>
                    </h3>



                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-7">
                            <strong>
                                Firma:
                                <address t-field="o.partner_id"
                                         t-options='{"widget": "contact", "fields": ["address", "name"], "no_marker": True}'/>
                            </strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-5">
                            <div class="text-right" style="background-color: red;">
                                <b>Projekt:
                                    <span t-field="o.name"/>
                                </b>
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-right">
                                Belegnummer:
                                <span t-field="o.number"/>
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-right">
                                Datum:
                                <span t-field="o.date_invoice" t-options='{"widget": "date"}'/>
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-right">
                                <br/>
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-right">
                                Ansprechpartner:
                                <span t-field="o.user_id"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right">
                                Telefon:
                                <span t-field="o.user_id.phone"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right">
                                Email:
                                <span t-field="o.user_id.login"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right">
                                Seite:
                                <span class="page"/>
                                /
                                <span class="topage"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>
                        Unsere Lieferantennummer:
                        <span t-field="o.name"/>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        FuÌˆr unsere Leistungen berechnen Ihnen wie folgt:
                    </p>

                    <!-- Is there a discount on at least one line? -->
                    <t t-set="display_discount" t-value="any([l.discount for l in o.invoice_line_ids])"/>

                    <table class="table table-condensed" name="invoice_line_table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Position</th>
                                <th>Bezeichnung</th>
                                <th class="text-right">Menge Einheit</th>

                                <th class="text-right">Einzelpreis
                                    <p style="color:green;">
                                        Rabatt %
                                    </p>
                                </th>

                                <th class="text-right">Nettosumme
                                    <p style="color:green;">
                                        Rabattbetrag
                                    </p>
                                </th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="invoice_tbody">
                            <tr t-foreach="o.invoice_line_ids" t-as="l">
                                <td>
                                    <span t-esc="l_index+1"/>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <span t-field="l.name"/>
                                </td>

                                <td class="text-right">
                                    <span t-field="l.quantity"/>
                                    <span t-field="l.uom_id"/>
                                </td>

                                <td class="text-right">

                                    <span t-field="l.price_unit" t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>

                                    <t t-if="l.price_subtotal_net2 !=l.price_subtotal">
                                        <p>
                                            <span t-field="l.discount"/>%

                                        </p>
                                    </t>

                                </td>

                                <td class="text-right" id="subtotal">

                                    <span t-field="l.price_subtotal_net2"
                                          t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>

                                    <t t-if="l.price_subtotal_net2 !=l.price_subtotal">
                                        <p>
                                            <span t-field="l.price_subtotal"
                                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                                        </p>
                                    </t>

                                </td>
                            </tr>

                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-6">

                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <strong>
                                Nettobetrag
                            </strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <strong>
                                Mwst
                            </strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <strong>
                                Bruttobetrag
                            </strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row" style="border: 1px solid black;">
                        <div class="col-xs-6">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <span t-field="o.amount_untaxed"
                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <span t-field="o.amount_tax"
                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-2">
                            <span t-field="o.amount_total"
                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <tr t-foreach="o.tax_line_ids" t-as="t">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-8">
                                <span t-field="t.tax_id.name"/>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-xs-2">
                                <span t-field="t.amount"
                                      t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-xs-4">

                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </tr>

                    <div class="clearfix"  style="display:none;">
                        <div id="total" class="row"  style="display:none;">
                            <div class="col-xs-4 pull-right">
                                <table class="table table-condensed" style="min-width: 250px;max-width: 400px;">
                                    <tr class="border-black" style="border-bottom:1px solid #dddddd;">
                                        <td>

                                        </td>
                                        <td class="text-right">
                                            <span t-field="o.amount_untaxed"
                                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <t t-foreach="o._get_tax_amount_by_group()" t-as="amount_by_group">
                                        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #dddddd;">
                                            <t t-if="len(o.tax_line_ids) == 1 and o.amount_untaxed == amount_by_group[2]">
                                                <td>
                                                    <span t-esc="amount_by_group[0]"/>
                                                    <span>&amp;nbsp;
                                                        <span>on</span>
                                                        <t t-esc="amount_by_group[4]"/>
                                                    </span>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="text-right">
                                                    <span t-esc="amount_by_group[3]"/>
                                                </td>
                                            </t>
                                            <t t-else="">
                                                <td>
                                                    <span t-esc="amount_by_group[0]"/>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="text-right">
                                                    <span t-esc="amount_by_group[3]"/>
                                                </td>
                                            </t>
                                        </tr>
                                    </t>
                                    <tr class="border-black">
                                        <td>
                                            <strong>Total</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="text-right">
                                            <span t-field="o.amount_total"
                                                  t-options='{"widget": "monetary", "display_currency": o.currency_id}'/>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p >
                        Zahlungsbedingungen:
                        <span t-field="o.payment_term_id"/>
                    </p>

                    <p style="background-color: red;">
                        Lieferbedingungen:
                        <span t-field="o.name"/>
                    </p>

                    <p t-if="o.comment">
                        <span t-field="o.comment"/>
                    </p>

                    <p >
                        Ware, soweit diese beauftragt wurde, bleibt bis zur vollstÃ¤ndigen Bezahlung unser Eigentum. Es gelten unsere Allgemeinen
                        GeschÃ¤ftsbedingungen und Datenschutzbedingungen. Diese sind im Internet unter www.hsl-tech.de einsehbar. Gerne lassen
                        wir Ihnen diese auch zukommen.
                    </p>



                </div>


            </xpath>

        </template>
    </data>
</odoo>